<H1>Our Clients</H1>

<P>Acknowledging the importance of providing quality indoor air for their staff and customers, the following organisation have engaged us to maintain the cleanliness of their air-ducts:
Far East Levingston, Ngee Ann Polytechnic, SmithKline Beecham Pharmaceuticals, National University of Singapore, Singapore General Hospital, Sheraton Towers, Manhattan Building and Singapore Polymer Corporation.
