<TD colspan=2 ALIGN=left VALIGN=top>
<H2>Ocak Isik Yurt&ccedil;u to receive International Press Freedom Award</H2>

<P>Yurtcu the imprisoned former editor in chief of<I> Ozgur Gundem</I>a
daily newspaper in Turkey closed by government pressure, for extraordinary
devotion to the principles of press freedom through extensive and balanced
reporting of the Kurdish conflict in principled defiance of Turkish government
censorship orders. 
<HR></P>
</TD>
</TR>

