<CENTER><P><!-- Link Tag --><!-- Graphic Tag --><A HREF="http://www.cpj.org/news/index.html"><IMG SRC="http://www.cpj.org/pictures/newsalert.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=104 WIDTH=452></A>
