<HEAD><TITLE>Press Freedom Report</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<CENTER><!-- Graphic Tag --><IMG  SRC="addis2"></CENTER>
<hr>
<p>

By <B>Kakuna Kerina</B><br>
Committee to Protect Journalists
<P>

<B><P>
<p>
