<blockquote>

<B>For Immediate Release</B><BR>
14 June 1996 <BR>
<BR>
<B>Contact:</B> <!-- MailTo Tag --><A HREF="MAILTO:europe@cpj.org">Catherine Fitzpatrick</A><BR>
