<blockquote>
<B>FOR IMMEDIATE  RELEASE</B><BR>
7 June 1996<br>
<br>
<B>Contact:</B><br><!-- MailTo Tag --><A HREF="MAILTO:europe@cpj.org"> Cathy Fitzpatrick</A><BR>
(212) 465-1004 x101<br>
<!-- MailTo Tag --><A HREF="MAILTO:aonion@cpj.org">Amanda Onion</A><BR>
