<DOCNO>WT01-B01-95</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000251-B020-51</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpj.org:80/urgent/ur0000002/background.html 169.132.35.44 19970108113905 text/html 4553
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
