<DOCNO>WT01-B01-102</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000251-B021-8</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpj.org:80/awards96/daoud.html 169.132.35.44 19970108114221 text/html 4743
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 11:42:10 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
