<BR>
Llosa, editor in chief of the newspaper <CITE>El Casmeno </CITE>
and a reporter with Radio Casma, was arrested in Casma and charged with involvement 
in a 1986 terrorist incident in Cuzco. A secret tribunal of the Superior Court of 
Cuzco convicted and sentenced him on Aug. 10 to six years in prison. Llosa is being 
held in the maximum security Yanamayo prison.<BR>
<BR>
