<STRONG>Faisal Allush<BR>
</STRONG>
<CITE>Imprisoned: </CITE>
1985<BR>
Allush, a journalist and political writer who has been in jail since 1985, was sentenced 
in June 1993 to 15 years' imprisonment for membership in the banned Party for Communist 
Action.<BR>
