 <CITE>M&uuml;cadele<BR>
</CITE>
<CITE>Imprisoned: </CITE>
1995<BR>
T&uuml;rk, a reporter for the leftist magazine <CITE>M&uuml;cadele, </CITE>
was arrested sometime in 1995 and is being held in a prison in Ankara.<BR>
<STRONG><BR>
</STRONG>
