<CITE>Place of Death: </CITE>
East of Algiers<BR>
Saidj, former editor in chief of the now-defunct independent weekly <CITE>El Ouma, </CITE>
was found dead in his car, about 15 kilometers east of Algiers. His throat had been 
slit. <BR>
<BR>
