<CITE>Place of Death: </CITE>
Reghaia<BR>
Sabour, a cultural reporter for the independent Arabic-language weekly <CITE>Echourouk al-Arabi </CITE>
and a contributor to a number of arts reviews, was shot to death by three men disguised 
as policemen at her family home in Reghaia, about 25 kilometers east of Algiers.<BR>
<BR>
