<CITE>Place of Death: </CITE>
Oran<BR>
Benaouda, a professor of Arabic at Oran University and a frequent contributor to many 
publications, including the government-run daily <CITE>El Djoumhouria, </CITE>
was shot to death in the evening by unknown assailants in the Delmonte quarter of 
the western city of Oran<BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>Mourad Hmaizi,</STRONG>
 <CITE>ENTV</CITE>
<BR>
