<CITE>Place of Death: </CITE>
Baraki<BR>
Unknown gunmen shot and killed Hmaizi, a reporter with state-run Algerian television 
(ENTV), as he was getting out of his car in front of his home in Baraki, a suburb 
of Algiers.<BR>
