<STRONG>Ahmed Takouchet,</STRONG>
 <CITE>Radio Cirta</CITE>
<BR>
<CITE>Date of Death: </CITE>
June 18, 1995<BR>
<CITE>Place of Death: </CITE>
Constantine<BR>
Takouchet, a journalist with Radio Cirta, the state-run radio station based in the 
