For the past year, Computer Motion has marketed the first FDA-cleared
robot for laparoscopic surgery. Over 80 hospitals have purchased
or leased the AESOP 1000. Since the initial introduction of the
product, acceptance has expanded to a point where over 800 procedures
are performed monthly in institutions around the country. A new
record is established every month.
