<DOCNO>WT01-B01-180</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA018-000194-B021-343</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.computermotion.com:80/TS_Page.htm 198.68.144.80 19970106153900 text/html 2413
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 06 Jan 1997 15:36:40 GMT
