<DOCNO>WT01-B01-181</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA018-000194-B021-357</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.computermotion.com:80/DS_Page.htm 198.68.144.80 19970106153908 text/html 2811
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 06 Jan 1997 15:36:47 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
