<h4>The Quarterly News Letter - Highlights</h4>

<LI><A HREF="#Partner">Computer Motion Partnering in MI Cardiac</A>
<LI><A HREF="#Message">Message from the President</A>
<LI><A HREF="#OR">Voice Control and the OR of the Future</A>
<LI><A HREF="#AESOP2">AESOP 2000... The Voice of the Future</A>
<LI><A HREF="#Shaun">Shaun Cleary, Director of US Sales</A>
<LI><A HREF="#BB">Bronwyn Byron, RN, BSN, CNOR</A>
