<body bgcolor=#ffffff>
<h2><img src="PINFO.gif" align=bottom width=219 height=41> <br>
</h2>
<p align=center><a href="pdescri.htm"><font size=3>Product Description</font></a><font size=3> | </font><a href="benefit.htm"><font size=3>Key Benefits </font></a><font size=3>| </font><a href="upgrade.htm"><font size=3>Upgrade Information</font></a><font size=3> | </font><a href="specs.htm"><font size=3>Specifications </font></a><font size=3>| </font><a href="info.htm"><font size=3>Request for More Info</font></a><font size=3> <br>
</font></p>
<h2 align=center>AESOP 1000 Specifications<br>
</h2>
<h3>Component Weights </h3>
<ul>
<li>Positioning Arm, 38 lbs </li>
<li>Controller, 19 lbs </li>
<li>Foot Control, 5 lbs </li>
<li>Hand Control, 1 lb </li>
</ul>
<h3>Component Sizes </h3>
<ul>
<li>Controller, 18&quot; x 15&quot; x 6&#189;&quot; </li>
<li>Foot Control, 8&quot; x 8&quot; x 2&quot; </li>
<li>Hand Control, 2&#189;&quot; x 4&quot; x 1&quot; </li>
</ul>
<h3 align=center><img src="specs.gif" align=bottom width=157 height=153><br>
</h3>
<h3>System Input Requirements </h3>
<ul>
<li>Voltage, 100-127 VAC, 187-266 VAC Switchable </li>
<li>Frequency, 50-60 Hz </li>
<li>Current, 2 AAC </li>
</ul>
<h3>Cart Specifications </h3>
<ul>
<li>Weight, 140 lb </li>
<li>Size, 25&quot; x 18&quot; x 40&#189;&quot; </li>
</ul>
