<I><B>Being on a 24-hour watch system sheds new light on the world.
I like seeing the sunrise occasionally and the sunsets are gorgeous.
The water is very blue and clear and standing watch on the bow
you can see phosphorescent critters stirred up by the bow wave.Cindy


