<DOCOLDNO>IA097-001044-B047-106</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://sea2.sea.edu:80/journals/jrtop3.htm 206.33.82.2 19970215110121 text/html 5691
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
