<HEAD>
<TITLE> Official Learn At Home Web Site:   Community Contents Page</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<P><body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<P><table border=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0> <tr valign=top><td rowspan=3><img src="ccnlearn.gif" width=155 height=80 border=0></td></td><td colspan=2><a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap/bbar"><IMG SRC="bbar.gif" width=215 height=20 BORDER=0 ISMAP></A></td></tr><tr valign=top><td rowspan=2><img src="comm.gif" width=55 height=60 border=0></td><td><img src="2tcomm.gif" width=160 height=35 border=0></td></tr><tr><td><img src="blank.gif" width=160 height=25 border=0></td></tr></table>
<P>
<P><center><BR>

<TABLE>
<TR valign=top><TD>
<P><center><a href="hslda.htm"><img src="hsldamed.jpg" width=167 height=122 border=0></a><br><b><a href="hslda.htm">Home School Legal Defense Association<br>(HSLDA)</a></b></center><p>The purpose of the Home School Legal Defense Association  is to bring together a large number of home schooling families so that each can have a low-cost method of obtaining quality legal defense. </p></TD><TD>
<P><center><a href="nheri/index.htm"><img src="nherism.gif" width=174 height=122 border=0></a><br><b><a href="nheri/index.htm">National Home Education Research Institute<br>(NHERI)</a></b></center><p>NHERI's web site on Learn@Home will encourage you and give you ammunition for demolishing myths about home schooling. Youll get research fact sheets, reports, newsletters, and commentaries. </p></TD></TR></TABLE>
<BR>
</center><BR>
<hr><BR>

