<center><b><i>National Center for Home Education</i></b></center>
<ul><li><b>Symposium Schedule</b>  Information to come soon.</li>
<li><b>News</b></li>
<ul><li><a href="news1.htm">The Great Tug-of-War: Balancing Family and Other Responsibilities</a></li>
